  "title": "general clerk",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>A pioneer in career development and coaching since 2015. Office located just opposite IMM building and Jurong East MRT.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will support bookkeeping tasks and handle customer enquiries via email and phone, working flexible hours in a part-time role.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare and maintain accurate bookkeeping records to support financial tracking</li><li>Respond promptly to customer enquiries through emails and phone calls to provide clear information and follow-up</li><li>Use basic accounting skills to record transactions and assist with financial documentation</li><li>Operate MS Office applications to organize data and communicate effectively</li><li>Demonstrate responsibility and honesty in managing tasks and confidential information</li><li>Communicate fluently in English to ensure clear and professional interactions</li></ul>",
